{
  "texts": [
    "Moon Landing 3.8 4.9 I believe the moon landings were faked.",
    "It is quite clear, when you look closely at the facts with a truly",
    "open mind, that we did not (and still do not) have the technology to transport humans into space any further than earth's orbit.",
    "For example, the Van Allen radiation belts would have killed any astronauts on the way.",
    "The moon landings were filmed in a studio to raise Americans' spirits after the Space Race."
  ]
}